                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "The next step is to classify the collected data based on the scenarios. Although this is trivial for datasets with relatively homogeneous components (OpenAI Summary, OpenAI WebGPT) or small query size (MTBench), this is quite challenging on larger and more complex ones. Therefore, we train a classifier to help us with this. The complete training details are in §B Based on the classifier, we are able to classify all the data we have collected."
